{"tid":2196243,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"楊老師襲警罪成判囚 眾籌50萬應付雙親醫療生活開支 不足一日已達標 宣布停止接收善款","createTime":"2020-09-09T17:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T12:40:54.000Z","uid":240362,"like":76,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"e239d1846adb9ed56e61ece5ae90247793a9baf4","tid":2196243,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T17:38:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pokman.yeung.12/posts/115885140247039\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpokman.yeung.12%2Fposts%2F115885140247039&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGEy1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=68e3d3fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pokman.yeung.12/posts/115885140247039</a><br />\n<br />\nPok Man Yeung<br />\n1h &middot; <br />\n【停止接收善款】<br />\n<br />\n各位，我是博文。9月9日凌晨我在個人社交媒體發布有關眾籌的貼文，引起巨大的迴響，是我始料不及的。<br />\n<br />\n感謝大家都抱打不平並願助我一臂之力渡過難關。由於現時數額已達標，本人認為必須即時停止接收各路友好的善款。<br />\n<br />\n社會上一直存在不同的聲音，部分人士不停對本人構成騷擾，有的更揚言會對我和家人不利。我想強調：清者自清，我心坦蕩蕩，一片向明月。欲加之罪，何患無辭？<br />\n<br />\n亂世之中，和而不同重要，而同理心，更顯寶貴。再次，感謝大家願伸出援手。"},{"pid":"9a7c67826249a618b77eb00c5db1b6afe5d0802f","tid":2196243,"uid":240362,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T17:38:30.000Z","msg":"【更新】<br />\n<br />\n港隊沙灘排球成員兼小學教師楊博文，去年11月11日駕車上班途中遭交通警截查，其間被指襲警，最終裁定罪成，是反修例運動以來首名襲警罪成的教師，更一度遭裁判官吳重儀還押小欖精神病治療中心。楊昨被判監九星期，但獲准繼續保釋等候上訴。他昨深夜在ig發文，自言已申請上訴，祈求法律能還他一個公道。他又謂「一直以來，我最擔心的不是自己的前途；要入獄，我唯一放心不下的是家中年老的雙親」，因他早前已遭校方解僱，經濟拮据，故希望眾籌50萬元，作為父母的醫療開支和生活費。<br />\n<br />\n事隔不足24小時，楊博文再次在社交媒體貼文，指眾籌貼文引起巨大迴響，他亦始料不及。他感謝各界抱打不平並願助他一臂之力，渡過難關。由於眾籌數額已達標，他已即時停止接收各路友好的善款。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200909/SESZ7DSHL5GPZM3KUMDNK2LNCQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200909%2FSESZ7DSHL5GPZM3KUMDNK2LNCQ%2F&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGEy1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=ed642a09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200909%2FSESZ7DSHL5GPZM3KUMDNK2LNCQ%2F&h=ed5fda87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200909/SESZ7DSHL5GPZM3KUMDNK2LNCQ/</a>"},{"pid":"18b0356791699b353d1d3be35604c0371bb26204","tid":2196243,"uid":46161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T17:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b10aae01dd53dc9db9784620ea655bf2cdab62f","tid":2196243,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18b0356791699b353d1d3be35604c0371bb26204","tid":2196243,"uid":46161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T17:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T17:39:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4e03ce2b31c7ed8d25a1678f79583a5824ed42","tid":2196243,"uid":104582,"like":5,"dislike":64,"score":-59,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T17:43:54.000Z","msg":"佢係慘,<br />\n但好似開左個壞既先例"},{"pid":"c9ef0216533feebb28e2ae13b5072a2003336212","tid":2196243,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T17:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc57ca60e97db5ba3b5560028b264a1ef4d66639","tid":2196243,"uid":249703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e4e03ce2b31c7ed8d25a1678f79583a5824ed42","tid":2196243,"uid":104582,"like":5,"dislike":64,"score":-59